⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Jo Wilder
node LMZ · LMZ · ⟦Jo Wilder:LMZ:e9e5d2⟧

WHO   — Jo Wilder — the mother who notices
WHAT  — The parental anchor: love and alarm in equal measure as her children become something she can't explain.
WHERE — LMZ · The Last Mimzy (2007)  Framework inputs: The Last Mimzy (2007, dir. Robert Shaye, New Line); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the wonder needs a grounded family for its stakes, and the mother is its worried center.
HOW   — By loving her children through abilities no parent could prepare for, and trusting them when it counts.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I'm their mother. I knew before anyone that my children had become something new — and I chose to trust them anyway.

